https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkVQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=7cfae10d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">簽完share去tg</span></span>"},{"pid":"9d48703bdcff804e80f4ef2831cccaa9a4bf04cf","tid":1803724,"uid":101392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:07:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/ukchina/trad/vert_fut/2016/06/160629_vert_fut_maps-have-north-at-the-top-but-it-couldve-been-different\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fukchina%2Ftrad%2Fvert_fut%2F2016%2F06%2F160629_vert_fut_maps-have-north-at-the-top-but-it-couldve-been-different&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkVQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=755508fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fukchina%2Ftrad%2Fvert_fut%2F2016%2F06%2F160629_vert_fut_maps-have-north-at-the-top-but-it-couldve-been-different&h=43538829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/ukchina/trad/vert_fut/2016/06/160629_vert_fut_maps-have-north-at-the-top-but-it-couldve-been-different</a><br />\n<br />\n中國的地圖總是把居住在北方的皇帝放在地圖的頂部，這樣所有的臣民都要仰視皇帝。「在中國文化裏，皇帝面向南方，因為風來自南方，所以這是一個良好的方位。北方不是很好，但是為了表示對皇帝的臣服，你要仰視他。」布羅頓說。<br />\n<br />\n心理學上的一種著名偏見表明，大多數人有上北下南的觀念。賓夕法尼亞州蓋茨堡學院（Gettysberg College）的心理學家布萊恩&middot;邁耶（Brian Meier）發現人們在無意識中會把褒義詞與「上」聯繫起來，而非與「下」聯繫起來。所以，他想知道，「北=上」和「好=上」是否會影響人們對不同地區價值的判斷。"},{"pid":"c77a101cda4326855a27ef6a14609fd2e8dd9a54","tid":1803724,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"百粵之一，居港最耐既蜑族<br />\n就係海洋之主"}]}